FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:4001

# Library API

API quản lý sách – demo so sánh API Blueprint vs OpenAPI.

## Books Collection [/books]

### Get all books [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
          { "id": 1, "title": "Doraemon", "author": "Fujiko Fujio", "year": 1969 },
          { "id": 2, "title": "The Great Gatsby", "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald", "year": 1925 }
        ]

### Create a new book [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "title": "New Book",
          "author": "Author Name",
          "year": 2024
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 3,
          "title": "New Book",
          "author": "Author Name",
          "year": 2024
        }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

        {
          "error": "Title, author and year are required"
        }

## Book [/books/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id (integer, required) - ID của book

### Get book by ID [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 1,
          "title": "Doraemon",
          "author": "Fujiko Fujio",
          "year": 1969
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
          "error": "Book not found"
        }

### Update a book [PUT]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "title": "Updated Title",
          "author": "Updated Author",
          "year": 2025
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 1,
          "title": "Updated Title",
          "author": "Updated Author",
          "year": 2025
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
          "error": "Book not found"
        }

### Delete a book [DELETE]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "message": "Book deleted"
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
          "error": "Book not found"
        }
